    "raw_text": "Letter of Support Request Form\nPlease fill out all required fields.\nWelcome to the Funding Letter of Support Request Form. Please complete the details below to help Representative Barb Gleim understand your project or initiative, including its objectives, anticipated outcomes, and the impact on your community. Your input is crucial in enabling the representative to craft a tailored letter of support for your funding application.\nApplicant\nApplicant Name\nIs the eligible applicant applying on behalf of another organization?\nYes\nNo\nGrant/Loan\nFunding Department, Agency, Bureau, etc.\nFunding Program\nType of Funding\nGrant\nLoan\nTax Credit\nProject Name\nMunicipality\nCounty\nRequested Amount\nTotal Project Cost\nBrief Description of the Project\nBrief Impact of the Project\nSupport Letter Handling\nTo whom should the letter be addressed/directed?\nPlease provide the organization/department/agency of the above addressee\nPlease provide the mailing address of the above addressee\nPA\nAA\nAE\nAK\nAL\nAP\nAR\nAS\nAZ\nCA\nCO\nCT\nDC\nDE\nFL\nFM\nGA\nGU\nHI\nIA\nID\nIL\nIN\nKS\nKY\nLA\nMA\nMD\nME\nMH\nMI\nMN\nMO\nMP\nMS\nMT\nNC\nND\nNE\nNH\nNJ\nNM\nNV\nNY\nOH\nOK\nOR\nPA\nPR\nPW\nRI\nSC\nSD\nTN\nTX\nUT\nVA\nVI\nVT\nWA\nWI\nWV\nWY\nSupport Letter Due Date\nPlease allow at least two fully operational business days.\nContact Information\nFirst Name*\nLast Name*\nPhone*\nEmail*\nAddress*\nCity*\nState*\nPA\nAA\nAE\nAK\nAL\nAP\nAR\nAS\nAZ\nCA\nCO\nCT\nDC\nDE\nFL\nFM\nGA\nGU\nHI\nIA\nID\nIL\nIN\nKS\nKY\nLA\nMA\nMD\nME\nMH\nMI\nMN\nMO\nMP\nMS\nMT\nNC\nND\nNE\nNH\nNJ\nNM\nNV\nNY\nOH\nOK\nOR\nPA\nPR\nPW\nRI\nSC\nSD\nTN\nTX\nUT\nVA\nVI\nVT\nWA\nWI\nWV\nWY\nZip*\nLeaving this box checked verifies that you would like to receive legislative email updates.\nChecking this box verifies that you consent to receive calls and SMS/MMS messages, including autodials and automated calls and texts, from Barb Gleim. Msg frequency will vary. Msg & data rates apply. Reply STOP to unsubscribe. Text HELP for support or\nclick here\n.\nPrivacy Policy\nDisclaimer: Submission of this request does not guarantee that a letter of support will be issued. All requests are subject to review, and the final decision to provide a letter of support rests solely with the representative and the relevant governing bodies.\nSubmit\nSign Up to Receive Legislative Email Updates\nKeep up-to-date on the latest legislative and community news. Your email address will be used strictly for legislative purposes.\nEmail*\nZIP Code\nSubscribe",
